title: Just carried a game where all my 4 teamates fed REAL bad

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body:
and when i mean real bad i mean really really really bad
and they were pretty bad in cases of map awareness and what to do when
almost as bad as my english, anyways lol:

Teammate #1 KDA 1/33/6
Teammate #2 KDA 2/22/7
Teammate #3 KDA 4/12/5
Teammate #4 KDA 7/14/4

i literally had to 1v3/4/5 all teamfights
most of the time none of them were even there
and the anivia cc, burst damage, and walls... ya... and also so many GA's and eggs (they were good anivias trust me)
i don't even play yasuo lmao

http://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/NA1/1989475575/201696587?tab=overview

anyways never give up  and always be nice to your teammates :3
